## Build output directory (intermediate artifacts)
logs/

## Generated PDF lives in examples/ — tracked intentionally
## Uncomment the next line only if you do NOT want to track the output PDF
# examples/main.pdf

## Source/working files (not part of the final document)
content/

## Mermaid generated images — live in examples/docs/diagrams/ (tracked intentionally)
## Ignore any PNGs/SVGs accidentally placed directly in the source diagrams folder
docs/diagrams/*.png
docs/diagrams/*.svg
## examples/docs/diagrams/ is NOT ignored — those are the tracked build artifacts

